## DT Publication Workflow (Topic 3)

Context: Publication state was implicit — no formal workflow state machine existed.
The MCP/API active toggle was manual (via Registry → Browse) and disconnected from
any publication concept. Domain sub-pages showed version but no lifecycle status.
The Domain Cockpit (Insights) was also missing domain/version context.

Changes:

1. src/back/objects/session/DomainSession.py
   Added `publication_status: "draft"` to the empty domain info template.
   Exported and imported via `export_for_save()` / `import_from_file()` following
   the same pattern as `mcp_enabled`.

2. src/back/objects/domain/Domain.py
   Added `_set_version_publication_status(svc, version, status)` internal method:
   transitions the publication state and, when status is `"published"`, automatically
   sets `mcp_enabled=True` on that version and clears it on all others.
   Added four public methods: `publish_version`, `deprecate_version`,
   `set_version_review`, `set_version_draft`.
   Updated `list_version_details()` to include `publication_status` per version.
   Updated `get_version_status()` to include `publication_status` for the loaded version.

3. src/api/routers/internal/domain.py
   Added four new endpoints:
   - POST /domain/publish — publish a version (auto-activates MCP)
   - POST /domain/deprecate — deprecate a version (deactivates MCP)
   - POST /domain/set-review — submit a version for review
   - POST /domain/set-draft — revert a version to draft

4. src/front/routes/dtwin.py
   Added `publication_status` to the dtwin template context, read from the session info.

5. src/front/templates/partials/dtwin/_query_sigmagraph.html
   src/front/templates/partials/dtwin/_query_reasoning.html
   src/front/templates/partials/dtwin/_query_chat.html
   src/front/templates/partials/dtwin/_query_dataquality.html
   src/front/templates/partials/dtwin/_query_cohorts.html
   src/front/templates/partials/dtwin/_query_graphql.html
   Added publication_status badge in sub-header after the version badge.
   Colors: Draft=grey, In Review=yellow, Published=green, Deprecated=red.

6. src/front/templates/partials/dtwin/_query_insights.html
   Added publication_status badge in section heading (Domain Cockpit).
   Added Domain and version line below the description.

7. src/front/static/domain/js/domain-versions.js
   Replaced mcp_enabled badge with publication_status badge.
   Added `_pubStatusBadge()` and `_pubTransitionButtons()` helpers.
   Added `publishVersion()`, `deprecateVersion()`, `setVersionReview()`,
   `setVersionDraft()`, and `_applyPublicationTransition()` functions.
   Transition buttons are shown per-state: draft→review/publish, review→publish/draft,
   published→deprecate, deprecated→draft (restore).

8. src/front/templates/partials/domain/_domain_versions.html
   Renamed table column from "MCP / API" to "Status".
   Removed the "change Active in Registry → Browse" guidance note (now automatic).

